  <div class="welcome">
    <h1>Let's Have a Party</h1>
    <h2>Social playlists for your next gathering.</h2>

    <ul><h3>Getting started is simple:</h3>
      <li>1. Set a date for your party</li>
      <li>2. Pick a few artists to set the mood for the event</li>
